<br>
I made a series of hotkeys, like clerics use.  I did one for each of my three stuns, and one for my nukes.  And, I used them.<br>
<br>
The group would see me keep the mob stunlocked, and know it was me.  Used to be, they'd know it's stunlocked, but not really say anything.<br>
<br>
Anyway...I'm now a very, very popular wizard for normal exp grind groups.  Almost every group I'm in, with people I've never grouped with end up at the end of the night with comments like:<br>
<br>
&quot;Damn, you're a *great* wizard.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Hey, Shiz, going to put you on my friends list, okay?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Jeez Shiz, you're really effective&quot;<br>
<br>
etc...<br>
<br>
So, I'd suggest trying it.  Make the hotkeys and use them.  Only once have I had someone complain about the spam, and he was an idiot anyway.<br>
<br>
It's all about being seen.<br>
<br>
